Date of Birth: February 9, 1873<br/>
Birthplace: Logan, Utah, USA<br/>
Ordained apostle: January 7, 1919<br/>
Death: July 30, 1939<br/>
<br/>
Born Feb. 9, 1873, at Logan, Cache Co., Utah, to Henry Ballard and Margaret Reid McNeil.
Ordained apostle Jan. 7, 1919, by Heber J. Grant, at age 45; died July 30, 1939, at Salt Lake City, Salt Lake Co., Utah, at age 66.